{"tid":465152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尿道炎反復發作，救命","createTime":"2017-11-11T08:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T06:17:52.000Z","uid":83993,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2100a2fdf765f7df8c8e5fb292f86686098551f3","tid":465152,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月尿道炎反復來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以前都系一年一兩次，近兩個月好似斷唔到尾甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。睇左婦科，吃左5日抗生素同止尿痛的藥，感覺改善左d,但係還是覺得下面有d赤赤痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而且好似尿頻尿急甘。開始買過塞下面的藥試過，改善左又來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。已經戒左海鮮，辣果d,而且近排未好曬都無同老公同房，點解仲系唔好？而且我吃得多抗生素覺得好似個胃唔舒服，已經吃左不少藥。各位姐妹，如果有經驗，請教下我點好，唔該！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cda809710cf988614ddeff143e7c684f26c74e","tid":465152,"uid":15548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"尿道入屎？"},{"pid":"d3669b8939dfc2e2ecae8f07d3728936fae10b51","tid":465152,"uid":138594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"D人話飲紅莓汁會有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8338d352cf55ba6b74d602ea7ed76bfeba1cd2","tid":465152,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"每日都要飲大量水<br />\n好似話益生菌同紅莓素個啲都有幫助"},{"pid":"afefc2eded447a91c3b8a2c3746fe8b920d2f415","tid":465152,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"打少D啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma